lead_paragraph: Jonathan Lucroy got a deal he liked, Carlos Beltran joined him in Texas and Jay Bruce and Rich Hill also moved Monday during an 18-swap frenzy at the trade deadline.

headline.print_headline: Deal 'Em Up! 18 Trades _ Beltran, Lucroy, Bruce, Moore Move
